{
  "stem": "25773.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were still amassing people from the workshop into the big queue to take them probably straight to Umschlagplatz and Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this Jewish policeman already knew the secret.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We still didn't realize what was happening, but had a fear-- noises, some news were getting through to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, we ran there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the whole lot of nearly 500 people-- women, men, young, some women took the children with them--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we, we hid there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very early at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe, maybe it was 12 o'clock, early-- 11:00.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- the whole day, we were sitting in these benches.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We, we couldn't stretch our legs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was crammed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we communicated with each other by talking to each other, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't move out of this, of the fear, that they might see-- the Germans might see us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we stayed there till we heard the noises, about 8:00 in the evening, about-- that, that they returned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nice voices, very jolly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to drink, the Germans, full of fun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we crawled out and went to our places-- where we, we could find our places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I found, I found my-- I, I found my stepmother waiting for me, and my father was already taken.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We, we didn't even see him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was taken with the little boy in his arms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when, when we came to the flat, we could see still the soup my stepmother-- the soup was still warm he was cooking for him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH] the soup, and all the little train, the little rag toys, which we made for the little boy, were spread all over the place.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
